4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring specialists with no prior knowledge. Over 16 weeks, students will attend three live online classes each week. The program covers essential topics such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Participants will also learn about compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. The class size is limited to 18 students to ensure personalized attention. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by multiple institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop